casebody.data:
In the Matter of COMMUNITY RELATED SERVICES, INC. (CRS), Respondent,
v.
NEW YORK STATE DEPARTMENT OF HEALTH et al., Appellants. Motion No: 2017-1063 Court of Appeals of New York. Decided on December 19, 2017

Motion for leave to appeal dismissed upon the ground that the order sought to be appealed from is not the final paper from which leave to appeal may be sought (see CPLR 5611 ).
